      "date": "2016-04-27 04:29:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThanks for the information Andreas. Yeah, it looks pretty promissing to combine the page cache allocation with cgroup limitation. But this patch is not suitable to do that. The patch 19729 is better. Currently, we are still working on QoS based on job ID TBF. And as expected, with patch 19729, the results looks pretty good. Much better than with this patch. We will look into cgroup limit after this problem is totally solved.",
