          "date": "2016-04-21 12:13:42.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-7982 osc: qos support for page cache usage",
        "message": "LU-7982 osc: qos support for page cache usage\n\nSometimes, the page cache usages on Lustre client is far from\nbalanced between different groups. This patch tries to solve\nthis problem by adding an new mechanism on OSC level. Different\nrequests of using page cache are classified according to job ID.\nAnd if multiple job IDs are asking for more page cache, the job\nID that has lowest page cache usage will has the top priority\nof using more page cache.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: If85220c36dae4323e751a71b73deeca214327cb6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
